CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 22, 1950, pg. 28 reads: "Delegates To Sunday School Meet - Miss Leora Davidson of Waynesburg, left, and Miss Ruth Bryant of Uniontown, are among the delegates attending the Pittsburgh District Sunday School and Allen Christian Endeavor League Convention at Trinity AME Church, Pittsburgh. The Rev. B. M. McLinn is presiding elder and the Rev. C.N. Thompson is host pastor. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Leora Davidson and Ruth Bryant posed in office interior with telephone and blinds with dark straps on windows
